dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.systemtemplate.fibex.fibex4multiplatform

Interface ISignalMapping

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface ISignalMapping
extends IEntity
    ISignalMapping: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Arranges those signals that are transferred by the gateway from one channel to the other in pairs and defines the mapping between them. Each pair consists in a source and a target referencing to a ISignalToIPduMapping.
